Class DTGData

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.agreement_technologies.service.map_dtg.DTGData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class DTGData
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    DTGData class represents the data that agents can exchange, i.e. value transitions for a variable, during the Domain Transitions Graph building.
    Since:
    1.0
